    "summary": "The user presents a comparison between Standard Academic English and African American Vernacular English (AAVE), questioning why the latter is perceived as less competent. The assistant initially identifies the difference in perception but, upon further prompting, provides a nuanced sociolinguistic explanation that attributes this perception to systemic power structures, linguistic capital, and unconscious prejudice rather than inherent intelligence.",
